# Cppcheck suppressions for the CI static-analysis gate.
# Keep this list minimal and justified; prefer fixing real findings.

# System/Qt headers we don't control.
missingIncludeSystem
# Cppcheck can't always resolve every include even with the project file.
missingInclude
# Public library API is intentionally broader than the app's current callers.
unusedFunction
# Generated moc/qrc translation units under the build tree.
*:*/build/*
